# Title: SugusGuard Apple-Update
# Description: Blacklist to block Apple updates for AdGuard Home / AdGuard Pro App
# This Blacklist can interrupt some services and/or some website functionalities you
# may use or like to use. Take care that you've your personal Whitelist in place.
# List-URL: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SugusGuard/Blacklists/main/Apple-Update
# Date: 2023-03-07
#
## APPLE UPDATES & UPDATE-CHECK IOS, IPADOS, TVOS, MACOS
